{"tid":706573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11歲童軍尼龍繩纏頸命危","createTime":"2018-06-18T04:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T04:47:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"131a7554240d32b31a2a54f7d5281be98f438ef7","tid":706573,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:14:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180618/20423682\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180618%2F20423682&d=PG4Oxvt61KFSqZ%2F8SnozV7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=dc3a951e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180618%2F20423682&h=d5ef242a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180618/20423682</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月18日 <br />\n<br />\n11歲童軍尼龍繩纏頸命危<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180618/large/18la5p05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180618%2Flarge%2F18la5p05.jpg&h=6fe569d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■男童昨送院搶救時已陷昏迷，目前情況危殆。劉柏麟攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】品學兼優的11歲男童昨日父親節在將軍澳日出康城寓所，被父親發現遭尼龍繩纏頸，其父慌忙為他鬆開及報警。男童送院時已陷入昏迷，在兒童深切治療部留醫，目前情況危殆。據悉，男童近日情緒上並無異樣，但參加童軍正學習繩結，警方正了解案件是吊頸自殺抑或意外。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n父親揭發　疑練繩結出事<br />\n<br />\n命危的男童姓潘，與家人同住日出康城三期緻藍天5座晶巒一個單位。據稱，就讀小學5年級的男童品學兼優，家人最近亦無察覺他有何不快或有輕生念頭。昨晨8時許，42歲潘父在寓所發現兒子被尼龍繩纏頸，立即替他解開尼龍繩及報警。救護車接報趕至時，男童已經陷入昏迷，被送往將軍澳醫院搶救，其後轉往聯合醫院兒童深切治療部留醫，情況危殆。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，由於警方在現場未有撿獲遺書，而男童最近參加童軍正學習繩結，警方並且在男童的電腦中，發現他曾經瀏覽過影音網站YouTube有關「纏頸自救」的網頁，目前正調查男童是否在練習繩結時發生意外抑或是吊頸自殺，不過初步相信事件並沒有可疑。<br />\n<br />\n■記者劉柏麟  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n百米小路僅3盞街燈<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n醉洋漢圖搶槍　傷5警"},{"pid":"c2465d89f8628d9d5106f39f0d90e7100577ae8b","tid":706573,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/Rg0VQY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FRg0VQY.jpg&h=cf2b8ceb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7848bb76bff7be7e54d26a4bc1ca48c75b611414","tid":706573,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae14de51bdd15ecae74c84ced59b3991ce754052","tid":706573,"uid":41915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:47:12.000Z","msg":"會唔會係個老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}